<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-18770] Fix flaky initializationError in ReplicationQuotasTest/RequestQuotaTest (thread leak)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-18770</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;An unexpected thread was detected in the recent CI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;ReplicationQuotasTest#initializationError&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;RequestQuotaTest#initializationError&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
org.opentest4j.AssertionFailedError: Found 1 unexpected threads during @BeforeAll: executor-ShareFetch ==&amp;gt; expected: &amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; but was: &amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt; &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Failed CI:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/actions/runs/13203924058&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/actions/runs/13203924058&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/actions/runs/13237077533/job/36944376672&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/actions/runs/13237077533/job/36944376672&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
