                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="17925713" author="chia7712" created="Mon, 10 Feb 2025 19:53:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The root cause of the test failures lies in the failure to close the &lt;tt&gt;ReplicaManager&lt;/tt&gt; within the &lt;tt&gt;testDelayedShareFetchPurgatoryOperationExpiration&lt;/tt&gt; method. This omission results in an unreleased thread from the purgatory, leading to subsequent integration test failures due to thread leaks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17925717" author="chia7712" created="Mon, 10 Feb 2025 19:59:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It is related to PR: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/18725/files#r1949798227&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/18725/files#r1949798227&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
